    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697540/extras/b4c7acec3ac230a219c96910c6865e3a.poster.avif?t=1737973215\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697540/extras/b4c7acec3ac230a219c96910c6865e3a.webm?t=1737973215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697540/extras/b4c7acec3ac230a219c96910c6865e3a.mp4?t=1737973215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>2045 年标志着地球气候变化的高峰。一些国家的意图无法克服在全球范围内向大气中过度排放有害物质的问题。地球人口的增加导致其需求的增加。工厂、汽车、垃圾填埋场和局部战争的排放量增加了。<br><br>全球变暖已达到顶峰，并因异常高温导致食物短缺。水和食物被加热的气氛烧毁，后来只能在地下种植园种植一些东西。因此，人们开始为在阳光下的位置而战。局部冲突演变为全球冲突。<br><br>地球上的人口开始迅速减少，各国纷纷建造“超级堡垒”——深入地球深处的巨大建筑。并且为了控制该区域，放置了自动炮塔，即使没有人也可以自动进行轮班。<br><br>最终，上一次使用核武器的全球冲突开始了，这导致了核冬天。这导致行星温度下降。随着温度的升高，人类作为一个物种的数量也减少了。几乎失去了 85% 的潜力。所有没有避难所的人都会立即或在一段时间后死亡。<br><br>尽管几乎所有的人类残余都被消灭了，但战争仍在继续。自动化系统仍在战斗和摧毁目标。地球上的大片地区被开采、污染并充满了大量的防御设施。<br><br>但几十年后，是时候浮出水面，建立新的生活了。堡垒管理系统开始遵循协议，随机选择守卫人员清理敌方设施区域。一个随机的人被唤醒并被派去执行任务。<br><br>他们必须发出最简单的武器，一套带有人工智能的防护服，5分钟的指导和6秒的射击场。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >上映时间——2058年，守护者</h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>读</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697540/extras/c398fbda51e560074c78629371afa1c8.poster.avif?t=1737973215\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697540/extras/c398fbda51e560074c78629371afa1c8.webm?t=1737973215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697540/extras/c398fbda51e560074c78629371afa1c8.mp4?t=1737973215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>搜集</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697540/extras/c3a09403780e132339b2fc4bf594153d.poster.avif?t=1737973215\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697540/extras/c3a09403780e132339b2fc4bf594153d.webm?t=1737973215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697540/extras/c3a09403780e132339b2fc4bf594153d.mp4?t=1737973215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>打印</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697540/extras/9a447c7cc69c39d310482c607859cf72.poster.avif?t=1737973215\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697540/extras/9a447c7cc69c39d310482c607859cf72.webm?t=1737973215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697540/extras/9a447c7cc69c39d310482c607859cf72.mp4?t=1737973215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>调整</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hvoya</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697540/extras/7742951534734e79aa4001d8f5366b88.avif?t=1737973215\" width=600 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rosa</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697540/extras/8ea6b5da59c8114ac344daaa31cc33a3.avif?t=1737973215\" width=600 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Verba</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697540/extras/858590122